{"id":18011,"date":"2022-12-31T04:24:45","date_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:24:45","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nd.wv3.net\/amg-car\/gx-460-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-cua-lexus.html"},"modified":"2022-12-31T04:24:45","modified_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:24:45","slug":"gx-460-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-cua-lexus","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/2022\/12\/31\/gx-460-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-cua-lexus\/","title":{"rendered":"GX 460 \u2013 LX 600, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i SUV c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Lexus"},"content":{"rendered":"<\/p>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<p>GX 460 mang \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc SUV thu\u1ea7n t\u00fay, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p s\u1ef1 sang tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Lexus trong khi LX 600 mang \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u201cth\u1ea3m bay\u201d cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n \u1edf h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf sau.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb sedan nh\u01b0ng SUV ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng xe \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc cho Lexus trong h\u01a1n 30 n\u0103m qua.  T\u1eeb GX \u0111\u1ebfn LX, h\u00e3ng xe sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb d\u00f2ng SUV n\u00e0y h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 doanh nh\u00e2n th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ea1t hay ch\u00ednh kh\u00e1ch th\u00edch tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u201cth\u1ea3m bay\u201d.  Trong khi LX c\u00f3 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n m\u1edbi sau 14 n\u0103m v\u1edbi 3 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n th\u00ec GX \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u1ede th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Lexus GX 460 v\u1eabn s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh h\u1ea1ng sang.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"GX 460 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p th\u00fa v\u1ecb trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac, khi chi\u1ebfc SUV h\u1ea1ng sang c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn n\u00e0y l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc duy nh\u1ea5t s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng khung g\u1ea7m r\u1eddi, mang \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh kh\u00f3.  \u0110\u1eb7c t\u00ednh v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh SUV thu\u1ea7n t\u00fay, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 sang tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a Lexus, khi\u1ebfn GX 460 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t.  M\u1eabu SUV h\u1ea1ng sang c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lexus t\u1ea1o ra v\u1edbi \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng 2 trong 1: s\u1edf h\u1eefu s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh.  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m sang tr\u1ecdng, m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0 trong th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1.\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon.png\" title=\"gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-300x188.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-600x375.png 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon.png 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">GX 460 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p th\u00fa v\u1ecb trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac, khi chi\u1ebfc SUV h\u1ea1ng sang c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn n\u00e0y l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc duy nh\u1ea5t s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng khung g\u1ea7m r\u1eddi, mang \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh kh\u00f3.  \u0110\u1eb7c t\u00ednh v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh SUV thu\u1ea7n t\u00fay, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 sang tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a Lexus khi\u1ebfn GX 460 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t.  M\u1eabu SUV h\u1ea1ng sang c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lexus t\u1ea1o ra v\u1edbi kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m \u201c2 trong 1\u201d: s\u1edf h\u1eefu s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh off-road v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb sang tr\u1ecdng, m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"- \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433046_797_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon.png\" title=\"1672433046_797_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433046_797_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-300x192.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433046_797_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-600x385.png 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433046_797_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon.png 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef L-finesse bao tr\u00f9m thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u1ee7a d\u00f2ng GX.  T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe Lexus, GX 460 s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh con su\u1ed1t c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn, \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n l\u00e0 c\u1ee5m \u0111\u00e8n chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng ba b\u00f3ng LED v\u00e0 d\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e8n LED \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb ban ng\u00e0y h\u00ecnh ch\u1eef L \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"- 2\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433046_924_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon.png\" title=\"1672433046_924_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433046_924_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-300x199.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433046_924_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-600x399.png 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433046_924_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon.png 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Ch\u1ea5t SUV tr\u1ee9 danh c\u1ee7a Lexus c\u00f2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111u\u00f4i xe vu\u00f4ng v\u1ee9c, g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c m\u1ea3ng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea3n s\u1eafc ri\u00eang.  Lexus trang b\u1ecb cho GX 460 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 off-road nh\u01b0: H\u1ec7 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9ng 4WD, thanh \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh KDSS, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng treo th\u00edch \u1ee9ng AVS, ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh Crawl Control, camera \u0111a \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh Multi-Terrain Monitor.  \u2026 Ngo\u00e0i ra, GX 460 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdn \u0111a \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh Multi-Terrain Select qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ednh n\u0103ng c\u00f9ng l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t: Mud&amp;Sand, Loose Rock, Mogul, Rock&amp;Dirt v\u00e0 Rock.  Khi c\u00e1c ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t l\u1ef1c k\u00e9o A-TRC s\u1ebd t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n b\u1ed5 m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch h\u1ee3p l\u00fd cho c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 sau.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"- 3\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_780_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon.png\" title=\"1672433047_780_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_780_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-300x199.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_780_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-600x399.png 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_780_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon.png 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh kh\u1ed1i vu\u00f4ng v\u1ee9c, nam t\u00ednh l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, mang \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1ebb sang tr\u1ecdng kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u da v\u00e0 g\u1ed7.  M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed trung t\u00e2m EMV 10,3 inch, \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n qua touch pad ph\u00eda d\u01b0\u1edbi.  H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u00e2m thanh v\u00f2m cao c\u1ea5p Mark Levinson 17 loa, c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 330 watt h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n mang \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u00ednh ph\u00f2ng di \u0111\u1ed9ng.  N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a GX 460 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ed5ng s\u1ea1c v\u00e0 \u1ed5 c\u1eafm \u0111i\u1ec7n: 2 c\u1ed5ng USB ph\u00eda tr\u00ean, m\u1ed9t c\u1ed5ng USB \u1edf h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf th\u1ee9 hai.  \u1ed4 c\u1eafm \u0111i\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u1edf h\u1ed9p trung t\u00e2m (DC 12V), c\u1ea1nh khoang h\u00e0nh l\u00fd (AC 220V), cho ph\u00e9p ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng s\u1ea1c v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"- 4\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_37_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon.png\" title=\"1672433047_37_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_37_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-300x188.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_37_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-600x376.png 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_37_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon.png 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Khu v\u1ef1c trung t\u00e2m c\u1ea7n s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed c\u00e1c n\u00fat thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00ednh n\u0103ng v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh, n\u00e2ng h\u1ea1 g\u1ea7m, thay \u0111\u1ed5i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng treo, ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 off-road, s\u01b0\u1edfi gh\u1ebf\u2026 M\u1ed7i n\u00fat l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng.  \u2013 C\u00e1ch b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Lexus GX 460 tr\u1ef1c quan, gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng thao t\u00e1c nhanh ch\u00f3ng khi c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"- 5\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_79_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon.png\" title=\"1672433047_79_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_79_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-300x199.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_79_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-600x399.png 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_79_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon.png 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">\u0110\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng trong d\u00f2ng SUV c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Lexus l\u00e0 LX 600. Thay v\u00ec m\u1ed9t phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, LX th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n ra v\u1edbi ba phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n: \u0110\u00f4 th\u1ecb \u2013 7 ch\u1ed7, gi\u00e1 8,1 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng;  F Sport \u2013 5 ch\u1ed7 gi\u00e1 8,35 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 VIP \u2013 4 ch\u1ed7 c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf sau h\u1ea1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng gia, gi\u00e1 9,21 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng.  Lexus LX 600 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng khung g\u1ea7m r\u1eddi t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 GX 460, \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng th\u00eam 20% d\u00f9 tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1ea3m 200 kg so v\u1edbi LX 570 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"- 6\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_952_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon.png\" title=\"1672433047_952_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_952_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-300x199.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_952_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-600x399.png 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_952_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon.png 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf L-finesse v\u1eabn chi\u1ebfm \u01b0u th\u1ebf tr\u00ean h\u00ecnh kh\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a LX 600 nh\u01b0ng t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n tinh t\u1ebf v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u01a1n, kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n s\u1ef1 g\u00f3c c\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 h\u1ea7m h\u1ed1 \u1edf phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n c\u0169.  L\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi 7 thanh n\u1ed5i, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ba chi\u1ec1u t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c li\u1ec1n m\u1ea1ch kh\u00f4ng vi\u1ec1n.  Lexus tinh ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e0y c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng thanh ngang, ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eebng milimet gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t cho kh\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 t\u0103ng \u00e1p k\u00e9p.  H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e8n LED 3 b\u00f3ng.  \u0110\u00e8n ch\u1ea1y ban ng\u00e0y ch\u1eef L n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p d\u1ea1ng ba chi\u1ec1u, s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5u k\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i so v\u1edbi phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea1o hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e2u theo t\u1eebng g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"- 7\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_532_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon.png\" title=\"1672433047_532_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_532_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-300x199.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_532_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-600x399.png 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_532_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon.png 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Ngo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a LX 600 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf ph\u1ea7n \u0111u\u00f4i vu\u00f4ng v\u1ee9c, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3 h\u1ecda \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf d\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e8n h\u1eadu.  Chi\u1ec1u cao xe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u00f4ng qua h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng AHC v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng treo th\u00edch \u1ee9ng AVS.  Theo \u0111\u00f3, kho\u1ea3ng s\u00e1ng g\u1ea7m xe c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh t\u1edbi 4 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9 cao bao g\u1ed3m: Normal, High 1, High 2 v\u00e0 LOW.  AHC c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi t\u01b0 th\u1ebf th\u00e2n xe n\u1eb1m ngang ho\u1eb7c th\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ee9ng, mang l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng treo t\u1ed1i \u01b0u, gi\u00fap th\u00e2n xe \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1nh l\u00e1i, t\u0103ng v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m t\u1ed1c.  H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng treo th\u00edch \u1ee9ng AVS s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng van \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed tuy\u1ebfn t\u00ednh, t\u1ea1o ra ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1ee9c th\u1eddi, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh, m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng khi di chuy\u1ec3n.  \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, l\u1ef1c gi\u1ea3m ch\u1ea5n c\u0169ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i theo t\u1eebng ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e1i, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u00e1i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1eebng s\u1edf th\u00edch c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"- s\u1ed1 8\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_231_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon.png\" title=\"1672433047_231_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_231_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-300x199.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_231_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-600x399.png 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_231_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon.png 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Nh\u1eefng tinh hoa trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Lexus \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eadp trung tr\u00ean m\u1eabu SUV \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng LX 600. N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u da v\u00e0 g\u1ed7 cao c\u1ea5p.  Bu\u1ed3ng l\u00e1i tr\u00ean LX m\u1edbi \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m Tazuna, cho ph\u00e9p ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i tr\u1ef1c quan h\u01a1n v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc xe.  M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh trung t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t nghi\u00eang 30 \u0111\u1ed9 theo h\u01b0\u1edbng xu\u1ed1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi.  C\u00e1c c\u00f4ng t\u1eafc li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh nh\u01b0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng MTS \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh nhanh ch\u00f3ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.  V\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a n\u1eb1m d\u01b0\u1edbi m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ti\u1ec7n d\u1ee5ng.  M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed 12,3 inch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1eb1m ngang t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i, duy tr\u00ec c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng khi l\u00e1i xe tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh\u2026<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"- 9\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_499_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon.png\" title=\"1672433047_499_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_499_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-300x200.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_499_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon-600x401.png 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672433047_499_gx-460-e28093-lx-600-bo-doi-suv-co-lon.png 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">\u1ede phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n VIP cao c\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t, h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 ph\u00eda sau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lexus ch\u0103m ch\u00fat \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eebng chi ti\u1ebft, trang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec7m v\u00e0 t\u1ef1a l\u01b0ng v\u1eeba v\u1eb7n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u1ed3i.  T\u1ef1a \u0111\u1ea7u k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1edbn.  Ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u Urethane m\u1ec1m c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 rung \u0111\u1ed9ng, tri\u1ec7t ti\u00eau nh\u1eefng rung \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu khi v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh.  H\u1ecda ti\u1ebft th\u00eau ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n VIP 4 ch\u1ed7.  H\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf sau c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u1eadp, ng\u1ea3, ch\u1ec9nh \u0111a v\u1ecb tr\u00ed.  Gh\u1ebf VIP tr\u00ean LX 600 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng gian th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n t\u1ed1i \u0111a v\u1edbi g\u00f3c ng\u1ea3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 48 \u0111\u1ed9, l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb NASA.  V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea1m k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ng\u1ed3i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cung c\u1ea5p kho\u1ea3ng du\u1ed7i ch\u00e2n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 1.100 mm.  C\u1eb7p m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed ph\u00eda sau k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc 11,6 inch, \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u0111a th\u00f4ng tin b\u00ean trong khoang l\u00e1i.  B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i SUV c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn GX 460 v\u00e0 LX 600 gi\u00fap Lexus kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u1ebf trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng h\u1ea1ng sang tr\u00ean ph\u1ea1m vi to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u.  T\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, GX 460 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 t\u1eeb 5,74 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng, LX 600 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 t\u1eeb 8,1 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng (\u0111\u00e3 bao g\u1ed3m VAT).<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\">Quang Anh <\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\">\u1ea2nh: Lexus Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>GX 460 mang \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc SUV thu\u1ea7n t\u00fay, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p s\u1ef1 sang tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Lexus trong khi LX 600 mang \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u201cth\u1ea3m bay\u201d cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n \u1edf h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf sau. Xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb sedan nh\u01b0ng SUV ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng xe \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":16727,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[75],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18011"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=18011"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18011\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/16727"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=18011"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=18011"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=18011"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}